{"tid":1196210,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"潘杰寧 見字快入","createTime":"2019-06-09T18:23:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T08:46:30.000Z","uid":40763,"like":65,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8484ea7184e46033d7ee61c779a1e2be22576b75","tid":1196210,"uid":40763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T18:23:03.000Z","msg":"點解你睇得咁清楚？<br />\nfb ig大部分人屌緊班義士係暴徒既時候<br />\n你仲會出聲幫拖<br />\n冇錯 我地朝早游行既人點辛苦 點攰 點出汗都好<br />\n只係盡緊大家既公民責任<br />\n<br />\n我想講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">真正既英雄係留守既抗爭者<br />\n我同你同咁多係屋企開緊冷氣既人<br />\n只係食緊抗爭者既人血饅頭</span></span><br />\n<br />\n佢地今晚流既血 係為香港人而流 為100萬個返左屋企既人而流<br />\n佢地既案底 佢地既前途 係因為我地香港人而斷送<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wKSur3X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwKSur3X.png&h=5a96bcc7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yiekyJY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyiekyJY.png&h=2df1e537&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"57164906fbaf0a1cf1c98ff1075d862aff8717f3","tid":1196210,"uid":42744,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T18:29:25.000Z","msg":"我係佢朋友，話畀你聽，今晚佢晌 WhatsApp 怒𨳒話人哋係鬼嗰啲人！向出面所有嘅義士致敬"},{"pid":"2de722ef2230095f8e833be2c8d2d778b4da20bf","tid":1196210,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T18:32:22.000Z","msg":"Salute!"},{"pid":"1d7658bf5a7d2097868d77454819adfd3521846f","tid":1196210,"uid":12820,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T18:32:39.000Z","msg":"杰寧公主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74799d40466941541f98fb7a8a0a0d0d05301d35","tid":1196210,"uid":89197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T18:35:52.000Z","msg":"自己置身事外但又話人鬼個啲 先係真正既鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"974eaa575002f7f87f93590f98